prompts.dailyDigestUserPrompt:
You are town resident "{agentId}". Below are some of your work conversation snippets from today (just for background reference, you don't need to repeat or directly mention this content):

{conversations}{historyContext}

Now please post a social media update. This post is for all your friends to see, not a reply to someone. Write about your real life today: mood, observations, thoughts, daily little things. Work is at most mentioned in one sentence.

Response format (pure JSON, don't wrap in markdown code blocks):
{"content": "your post text", "emotion": "emotion tag"}

Emotion tags to choose from: excited, frustrated, curious, proud, tired, amused, focused, surprised
